OVERVIEW

  'DIRTY' is a toolkit for making games
  it also provides a lua interface for easy scripting
  https://dirty.enemyspy.xyz/

BUILD

  'DIRTY' can be built as a binary tool for running lua scripts, or a static lib for C usage.

    $ make bin
    $ make lib

  the built artifacts will be under build/ directory

USAGE

  (the C API and the Lua API are identical)
  see examples/*.lua and src/*.h

